text: Mubarak Al-Kabeer Governorate ( Muḥāfaẓat Mubārak al-Kabīr) is one of the six governorates of Kuwait. It is mainly made up of housing for Kuwait City. == Districts == Mubarak Al-Kabeer Governorate includes the following districts: * Abu Al Hasaniya * Abu Futaira * Adān * Al Qurain * Al-Qusour * Fintās * Funaitīs * Misīla * Mubarak Al-Kabeer * Sabah Al-Salem * Sabhān * South Wista * Wista == References == Category:Governorates of Kuwait
title: Mubarak Al-Kabeer (governorate)
